Job Description
Provide field service support for automatic transfer switch and monitoring system (maintenance, testing & commissioning, troubleshooting & repair).
Provide quality service and timely follow-up with customers.
Provide recommendation and quotation for repair or parts replacement work.
Plan and schedule task assigned by supervisor or manager.
Job Requirements
Candidate must possess at least a Diploma in Electrical, Power, Electronic or equivalent.
2-3 years of working experiences in Switch board, PLC or equivalent field is preferred.
Proficient in handling technical and service issue.
Ability to work independently.
Strong analytical skill and resourceful in problem solving.
Team player with good discipline and positive work attitude
Customer oriented and has passion for service.
Good interpersonal and customer relation skills.
